From 47819a01fd6f190d04644d36b6b4529381aa0204 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Super Z <super-z@local>
Date: Tue, 30 Jun 2026 11:24:28 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] =?UTF-8?q?feat(reasoning):=20add=20reasoning-first=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?protocol=20v1=20=E2=80=94=20plan/critique/execute/reflect?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Turns Hermes-Omni from a tool-dispatch loop into a reasoning-first agent.
The framework now FORCES the LLM to think before consequential actions,
while preventing recklessness through context-aware safety (LLM-as-judge),
not regex.

This is the bridge between 'unlimited mode' (no safety, reckless) and
'pattern-block mode' (regex can't reason). The agent has the appearance
of unlimited autonomy while maintaining a context-aware safety net that
scales with the LLM's intelligence.

New modules under agent/unified/:
  - decision.py     — DecisionFramework classifies actions by consequence
                      (TRIVIAL / STANDARD / CONSEQUENTIAL / IRREVERSIBLE)
  - reasoning.py    — ReasoningProtocol: plan → critique → reflect
                      Single LLM call per phase. Fail-open everywhere.
  - smart_guardian.py — LLM-as-judge guardian with cache + TTL.
                      ALLOW/WARN/REQUIRE_USER_CONFIRM/BLOCK verdicts.
                      Hard floor for IRREVERSIBLE by default.

New tools (tools/reasoning_tools.py):
  - reasoning_plan     — record explicit plan before action
  - reasoning_critique — record self-critique
  - reasoning_decide   — make auditable decision (escape hatch for hard floor)
  - reasoning_reflect  — record post-action reflection (persisted to reflexion store)

Modified:
  - agent/unified/config.py — 6 new config fields with env var overrides
  - agent/unified/integration.py — wired reasoning + smart guardian into
        before_tool_call/after_tool_call; added configure_reasoning_stack()
        public API; updated framework_status() with new flags
  - agent/omni_integration.py — marked deprecated, points to agent/unified/

Design doc: docs/REASONING_DESIGN.md

All new behavior is opt-in (default OFF). Legacy Hermes behavior unchanged.
Config flags:
  unified.reasoning.enabled: false (default)
  unified.smart_guardian.enabled: false (default)
  unified.smart_guardian.hard_block_irreversible: true (default)
  HERMES_UNIFIED_REASONING=1 / HERMES_UNIFIED_SMART_GUARDIAN=1 (env overrides)

Smoke tested: classification, graceful degradation without LLM, mock LLM
plan+verdict+cache hit. Formal tests to be added to tests/unified/.
